=== Keyboard Shortcuts

Keyboard Shortcuts allow you to perform common editing tasks.

With the focus in an editor,

press _Ctrl-Alt-H_ on Windows or Linux (when an editor has the keyboard focus) to popup the list of keyboard shortcuts.

Press _Cmd-Alt-H_ on Mac (when an editor has the keyboard focus) to popup the list of keyboard shortcuts.

Press _Esc_ to close the keyboard shortcuts.